#: src/license.cpp:89
#, kde-format
msgid "Commercial use"
msgstr "Komerčné použitie"

#: src/license.cpp:90 src/license.cpp:124
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The licensed material and derivatives may be used for commercial purposes."
msgstr ""
"Licencovaný materiál a odvodené diela sa môžu používať na komerčné účely."

#: src/license.cpp:94
#, kde-format
msgid "Modification"
msgstr "Zmena"

#: src/license.cpp:95
#, kde-format
msgid "The licensed material may be modified."
msgstr "Licencovaný materiál sa môže upravovať."

#: src/license.cpp:99
#, kde-format
msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "Rozdelenie"

#: src/license.cpp:100
#, kde-format
msgid "The licensed material may be distributed."
msgstr "Licencovaný materiál sa môže šíriť."

#: src/license.cpp:104
#, kde-format
msgid "Private use"
msgstr "Súkromné použitie"

#: src/license.cpp:105
#, kde-format
msgid "The licensed material may be used and modified in private."
msgstr "Licencovaný materiál sa môže používať a upravovať súkromne."

#: src/license.cpp:109 src/license.cpp:182
#, kde-format
msgid "Patent use"
msgstr "Použitie patentov"

#: src/license.cpp:110
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The licensed provides and express grant of patent rights from contributors."
msgstr ""
"Licencia poskytuje výslovné udelenie patentových práv od prispievateľov."

#: src/license.cpp:123
#, kde-format
msgid "License and copyright notice"
msgstr "Licencia a oznámenie o autorských právach"

#: src/license.cpp:128
#, kde-format
msgid "State changes"
msgstr "Uvádzanie zmien"

#: src/license.cpp:129
#, kde-format
msgid "Changes made to the licensed material must be documented."
msgstr "Zmeny vykonané v licencovanom materiáli musia byť zdokumentované."

#: src/license.cpp:133
#, kde-format
msgid "Disclose source"
msgstr "Sprístupnenie zdrojového kódu"

#: src/license.cpp:134
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Source code must be made available when the licensed material is distributed."
msgstr ""
"Zdrojový kód musí byť sprístupnený pri distribúcii licencovaného materiálu."

#: src/license.cpp:138
#, kde-format
msgid "Network use is distribution"
msgstr "Sieťové použitie je distribúcia"

#: src/license.cpp:139
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Users who interact with the licensed material via network are given the "
"right to receive a copy of the source code."
msgstr ""
"Používatelia, ktorí interagujú s licencovaným materiálom cez sieť, majú "
"právo získať kópiu zdrojového kódu."

#: src/license.cpp:143
#, kde-format
msgid "Same license"
msgstr "Rovnaká licencia"

#: src/license.cpp:144
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Modifications must be released under the same license when distributing the "
"licensed material. In some cases a similar or related license may be used."
msgstr ""
"Úpravy musia byť vydané pod rovnakou licenciou pri distribúcii licencovaného "
"materiálu. V niektorých prípadoch môže byť použitá podobná alebo súvisiaca "
"licencia."

#: src/license.cpp:148
#, kde-format
msgid "Same license (library)"
msgstr "Rovnaká licencia (knižnica)"

#: src/license.cpp:149
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Modifications must be released under the same license when distributing the "
"licensed material. In some cases a similar or related license may be used, "
"or this condition may not apply to works that use the licensed material as a "
"library."
msgstr ""
"Úpravy musia byť vydané pod rovnakou licenciou pri distribúcii licencovaného "
"materiálu. V niektorých prípadoch môže byť použitá podobná alebo súvisiaca "
"licencia, alebo sa táto podmienka nemusí vzťahovať na diela, ktoré používajú "
"licencovaný materiál ako knižnicu."

#: src/license.cpp:153
#, kde-format
msgid "Same license (file)"
msgstr "Rovnaká licencia (súbor)"

#: src/license.cpp:154
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Modifications of existing files must be released under the same license when "
"distributing the licensed material. In some cases a similar or related "
"license may be used."
msgstr ""
"Úpravy existujúcich súborov musia byť vydané pod rovnakou licenciou pri "
"distribúcii licencovaného materiálu. V niektorých prípadoch môže byť použitá "
"podobná alebo súvisiaca licencia."

#: src/license.cpp:167
#, kde-format
msgid "Liability"
msgstr "Pasíva"

#: src/license.cpp:168
#, kde-format
msgid "This license includes a limitation of liability."
msgstr "Táto licencia zahŕňa obmedzenie zodpovednosti."

#: src/license.cpp:172
#, kde-format
msgid "Warranty"
msgstr "Warranty"

#: src/license.cpp:173
#, kde-format
msgid "This license explicitly states that it does NOT provide any warranty."
msgstr "Táto licencia výslovne uvádza, že neposkytuje žiadnu záruku."

#: src/license.cpp:177
#, kde-format
msgid "Trademark use"
msgstr "Použitie ochrannej známky"

#: src/license.cpp:178
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This license explicitly states that it does NOT grant trademark rights, even "
"though licenses without such a statement probably do not grant any implicit "
"trademark rights."
msgstr ""
"Táto licencia výslovne uvádza, že NEudeľuje práva na ochrannú známku, hoci "
"licencie bez takéhoto vyhlásenia pravdepodobne neudeľujú žiadne implicitné "
"práva na ochrannú známku."

#: src/license.cpp:183
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This license explicitly states that it does NOT grant any rights in the "
"patents of contributors."
msgstr ""
"Táto licencia výslovne uvádza, že NEudeľuje žiadne práva na patenty "
"prispievateľov."

#: src/license.cpp:193
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"For REUSE compliance, copy the text of the license into a file named %1.txt, "
"it must be placed in the LICENSES/ directory in the root of your source code."
msgstr ""
"Pre súlad s REUSE skopírujte text licencie do súboru s názvom %1.txt, ktorý "
"musí byť umiestnený v adresári LICENSES/ na najvyššej úrovni repozitára."

#: src/license.cpp:196
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The Academic Free License is a variant of the Open Software License that "
"does not require that the source code of derivative works be disclosed. It "
"contains explicit copyright and patent grants and reserves trademark rights "
"in the author."
msgstr ""
"Academic Free License je variant Open Software License, ktorý nevyžaduje "
"sprístupnenie zdrojového kódu odvodených diel."

#: src/license.cpp:197
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file. Files "
"licensed under AFL 3.0 must also include the notice \"Licensed under the "
"Academic Free License version 3.0\" adjacent to the copyright notice."
msgstr ""
"Vytvorte textový súbor (zvyčajne s názvom LICENSE alebo LICENSE.txt) v "
"koreňovom adresári zdrojového kódu a skopírujte doň text licencie."

#: src/license.cpp:199
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A permissive license whose main conditions require preservation of copyright "
"and license notices. Contributors provide an express grant of patent rights. "
"Licensed works, modifications, and larger works may be distributed under "
"different terms and without source code."
msgstr ""
"Permisívna licencia, ktorej hlavné podmienky vyžadujú zachovanie oznámení o "
"autorských právach a licencii. Prispievatelia poskytujú výslovné udelenie "
"patentových práv. Licencované diela, úpravy a väčšie diela môžu byť šírené "
"pod inými podmienkami a bez zdrojového kódu."

#: src/license.cpp:200 src/license.cpp:218 src/license.cpp:221
#: src/license.cpp:230 src/license.cpp:233 src/license.cpp:239
#: src/license.cpp:245 src/license.cpp:251 src/license.cpp:254
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file."
msgstr ""
"Vytvorte textový súbor (zvyčajne s názvom LICENSE alebo LICENSE.txt) v "
"koreňovom adresári zdrojového kódu a skopírujte doň text licencie."

#: src/license.cpp:202
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The BSD Zero Clause license goes further than the BSD 2-Clause license to "
"allow you unlimited freedom with the software without requirements to "
"include the copyright notice, license text, or disclaimer in either source "
"or binary forms."
msgstr ""
"Licencia BSD Zero Clause ide ďalej ako licencia BSD 2-Clause a poskytuje vám "
"neobmedzenú slobodu so softvérom bez požiadaviek na zahrnutie oznámenia o "
"autorských právach, textu licencie alebo vyhlásenia v zdrojovej alebo "
"binárnej forme."

#: src/license.cpp:203
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"do not translate the placeholders e.g [year], [fullname] as they refer to "
"the untranslated original license"
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file.  Replace "
"[year] with the current year and [fullname] with the name (or names) of the "
"copyright holders. You may take the additional step of removing the "
"copyright notice."
msgstr ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file.  Replace "
"[year] with the current year and [fullname] with the name (or names) of the "
"copyright holders. You may take the additional step of removing the "
"copyright notice."

#: src/license.cpp:205
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A permissive license that comes in two variants, the BSD 2-Clause and BSD 3-"
"Clause. Both have very minute differences to the MIT license."
msgstr ""
"Permisívna licencia, ktorá existuje v dvoch variantoch, BSD 2-Clause a BSD 3-"
"Clause. Oba majú veľmi malé rozdiely oproti licencii MIT."

#: src/license.cpp:206 src/license.cpp:209 src/license.cpp:212
#: src/license.cpp:248
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"do not translate the placeholders e.g [year], [fullname] as they refer to "
"the untranslated original license"
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file. Replace "
"[year] with the current year and [fullname] with the name (or names) of the "
"copyright holders."
msgstr ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file. Replace "
"[year] with the current year and [fullname] with the name (or names) of the "
"copyright holders."

#: src/license.cpp:208
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A permissive license similar to the BSD 2-Clause License, but with a 3rd "
"clause that prohibits others from using the name of the project or its "
"contributors to promote derived products without written consent."
msgstr ""
"Permisívna licencia podobná licencii BSD 2-Clause, ale s 3. klauzulou, ktorá "
"zakazuje ostatným používať meno držiteľa autorských práv alebo jeho "
"prispievateľov na propagáciu odvodených produktov bez písomného súhlasu."

#: src/license.cpp:211
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A variant of the BSD 3-Clause License that explicitly does not grant any "
"patent rights."
msgstr ""
"Variant licencie BSD 3-Clause, ktorý výslovne neudeľuje žiadne patentové "
"práva."

#: src/license.cpp:214
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A permissive license similar to the BSD 3-Clause License, but with an "
"\"advertising clause\" that requires an acknowledgment of the original "
"source in all advertising material."
msgstr ""
"Permisívna licencia podobná licencii BSD 3-Clause, ale s „reklamnou "
"klauzulou“, ktorá vyžadovala, aby všetky reklamy uvádzajúce funkcie alebo "
"použitie softvéru zobrazovali konkrétne uznanie pôvodného tvorcu."

#: src/license.cpp:215
#, kde-format
msgctxt ""
"do not translate the placeholders e.g [year], [fullname] as they refer to "
"the untranslated original license"
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file. Replace "
"[year] with the current year and [fullname] with the name (or names) of the "
"copyright holders. Replace [project] with the project organization, if any, "
"that sponsors this work."
msgstr ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file. Replace "
"[year] with the current year and [fullname] with the name (or names) of the "
"copyright holders. Replace [project] with the project organization, if any, "
"that sponsors this work."

#: src/license.cpp:217
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A simple permissive license only requiring preservation of copyright and "
"license notices for source (and not binary) distribution. Licensed works, "
"modifications, and larger works may be distributed under different terms and "
"without source code."
msgstr ""
"Jednoduchá permisívna licencia vyžadujúca iba zachovanie oznámení o "
"autorských právach a licencii pre distribúciu zdrojového kódu (nie binárnu). "
"Licencované diela, úpravy a väčšie diela môžu byť šírené pod inými "
"podmienkami a bez zdrojového kódu."

#: src/license.cpp:220
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The Creative Commons CC0 Public Domain Dedication waives copyright interest "
"in a work you've created and dedicates it to the world-wide public domain. "
"Use CC0 to opt out of copyright entirely and ensure your work has the widest "
"reach. As with the Unlicense and typical software licenses, CC0 disclaims "
"warranties. CC0 is very similar to the Unlicense."
msgstr ""
"Venovanie Creative Commons CC0 do verejného vlastníctva sa vzdáva záujmu o "
"autorské práva na dielo, ktoré ste vytvorili, a venuje ho celosvetovému "
"verejnému vlastníctvu."

#: src/license.cpp:223
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Permits almost any use subject to providing credit and license notice. "
"Frequently used for media assets and educational materials. The most common "
"license for Open Access scientific publications. Not recommended for "
"software."
msgstr ""
"Povoľuje takmer akékoľvek použitie pod podmienkou uvedenia kreditu a "
"oznámenia o licencii. Často sa používa pre mediálne aktíva a vzdelávacie "
"materiály."

#: src/license.cpp:224 src/license.cpp:227
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named LICENSE or LICENSE.txt) in the root of "
"your source code and copy the text of the license into the file. It is also "
"acceptable to solely supply a link to a copy of the license, usually to the "
"canonical URL for the license."
msgstr ""
"Vytvorte textový súbor (zvyčajne s názvom LICENSE alebo LICENSE.txt) v "
"koreňovom adresári zdrojového kódu a skopírujte doň text licencie."

#: src/license.cpp:226
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Similar to CC-BY-4.0 but requires derivatives be distributed under the same "
"or a similar, compatible license. Frequently used for media assets and "
"educational materials. A previous version is the default license for "
"Wikipedia and other Wikimedia projects. Not recommended for software."
msgstr ""
"Podobné CC-BY-4.0, ale vyžaduje, aby odvodené diela boli šírené pod rovnakou "
"alebo podobnou kompatibilnou licenciou."

#: src/license.cpp:229
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This commercially-friendly copyleft license provides the ability to "
"commercially license binaries; a modern royalty-free patent license grant; "
"and the ability for linked works to use other licenses, including commercial "
"ones."
msgstr ""
"This commercially-friendly copyleft license provides the ability to "
"commercially license binaries; a modern royalty-free patent license grant; "
"and the ability for linked works to use other licenses, including commercial "
"ones."

#: src/license.cpp:232
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The GNU GPL is the most widely used free software license and has a strong "
"copyleft requirement. When distributing derived works, the source code of "
"the work must be made available under the same license. There are multiple "
"variants of the GNU GPL, each with different requirements."
msgstr ""
"GNU GPL je najpoužívanejšia licencia slobodného softvéru so silnou "
"copyleftovou požiadavkou. Pri distribúcii odvodených diel musí byť zdrojový "
"kód diela sprístupnený pod rovnakou licenciou."

#: src/license.cpp:235
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Permissions of this strong copyleft license are conditioned on making "
"available complete source code of licensed works and modifications, which "
"include larger works using a licensed work, under the same license. "
"Copyright and license notices must be preserved. Contributors provide an "
"express grant of patent rights."
msgstr ""
"Oprávnenia tejto silnej copyleftovej licencie sú podmienenéé sprístupnením "
"kompletného zdrojového kódu licencovaných diel a úprav, vrátane väčších diel "
"používajúcich licencované dielo, pod rovnakou licenciou."

#: src/license.cpp:236
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named COPYING, as per GNU conventions) in the "
"root of your source code and copy the text of the license into the file."
msgstr ""
"Vytvorte textový súbor (zvyčajne s názvom COPYING, podľa konvencií GNU) v "
"koreňovom adresári zdrojového kódu a skopírujte doň text licencie."

#: src/license.cpp:238
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Primarily used for software libraries, the GNU LGPL requires that derived "
"works be licensed under the same license, but works that only link to it do "
"not fall under this restriction. There are two commonly used versions of the "
"GNU LGPL."
msgstr ""
"Primárne používaná pre softvérové knižnice, GNU LGPL vyžaduje, aby odvodené "
"diela boli licencované pod rovnakou licenciou, ale diela, ktoré na ňu iba "
"odkazujú, pod toto obmedzenie nespadajú."

#: src/license.cpp:241
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Permissions of this copyleft license are conditioned on making available "
"complete source code of licensed works and modifications under the same "
"license or the GNU GPLv3. Copyright and license notices must be preserved. "
"Contributors provide an express grant of patent rights. However, a larger "
"work using the licensed work through interfaces provided by the licensed "
"work may be distributed under different terms and without source code for "
"the larger work."
msgstr ""
"Oprávnenia tejto copyleftovej licencie sú podmienenéé sprístupnením "
"kompletného zdrojového kódu licencovaných diel a úprav pod rovnakou "
"licenciou alebo GNU GPLv3."

#: src/license.cpp:242
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"This license is an additional set of permissions to the GNU GPLv3 license. "
"Follow the instructions to apply the GNU GPLv3, in the root of your source "
"code. Then add another file named COPYING.LESSER and copy the text."
msgstr ""
"Táto licencia je dodatočný súbor oprávnení k licencii GNU GPLv3. Postupujte "
"podľa pokynov licencie GPLv3 a zahrňte toto dodatočné oznámenie o "
"oprávneniach."

#: src/license.cpp:244
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Permissions of this strongest copyleft license are conditioned on making "
"available complete source code of licensed works and modifications, which "
"include larger works using a licensed work, under the same license. "
"Copyright and license notices must be preserved. Contributors provide an "
"express grant of patent rights. When a modified version is used to provide a "
"service over a network, the complete source code of the modified version "
"must be made available."
msgstr ""
"Oprávnenia tejto najsilnejšej copyleftovej licencie sú podmienenéé "
"sprístupnením kompletného zdrojového kódu licencovaných diel a úprav, "
"vrátane väčších diel používajúcich licencované dielo, pod rovnakou "
"licenciou. Oznámenia o autorských právach a licencii musia byť zachované."

#: src/license.cpp:247
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A short and simple permissive license with conditions only requiring "
"preservation of copyright and license notices. Licensed works, "
"modifications, and larger works may be distributed under different terms and "
"without source code."
msgstr ""
"Krátka a jednoduchá permisívna licencia s podmienkami vyžadujúcimi iba "
"zachovanie oznámení o autorských právach a licencii. Licencované diela, "
"úpravy a väčšie diela môžu byť šírené pod inými podmienkami a bez zdrojového "
"kódu."

#: src/license.cpp:250
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Permissions of this weak copyleft license are conditioned on making "
"available source code of licensed files and modifications of those files "
"under the same license (or in certain cases, one of the GNU licenses). "
"Copyright and license notices must be preserved. Contributors provide an "
"express grant of patent rights. However, a larger work using the licensed "
"work may be distributed under different terms and without source code for "
"files added in the larger work."
msgstr ""
"Oprávnenia tejto slabej copyleftovej licencie sú podmienenéé sprístupnením "
"zdrojového kódu licencovaných diel a úprav pod rovnakou licenciou alebo GNU "
"GPLv3. Oznámenia o autorských právach a licencii musia byť zachované."

#: src/license.cpp:253
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The easiest license out there. It gives the user permissions to do whatever "
"they want with your code."
msgstr ""
"Najjednoduchšia dostupná licencia. Dáva používateľovi oprávnenia robiť s "
"vaším kódom čokoľvek, pokiaľ vám prisudzujú zásluhy a neberú vás na "
"zodpovednosť."

#: src/license.cpp:256
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"A license with no conditions whatsoever which dedicates works to the public "
"domain. Unlicensed works, modifications, and larger works may be distributed "
"under different terms and without source code."
msgstr ""
"Licencia bez akýchkoľvek podmienok, ktorá venuje diela do verejného "
"vlastníctva. Nelicencované diela, úpravy a väčšie diela môžu byť šírené pod "
"inými podmienkami a bez zdrojového kódu."

#: src/license.cpp:257
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"Create a text file (typically named UNLICENSE or UNLICENSE.txt) in the root "
"of your source code and copy the text of the license disclaimer into the "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Vytvorte textový súbor (zvyčajne s názvom UNLICENSE alebo UNLICENSE.txt) v "
"koreňovom adresári zdrojového kódu a skopírujte doň text licencie."

